values:
Sometimes all somebody has to say is one little thing. 
One wrong adjective in the wrong place changes the air. 
You question this person, make sure that's the word that was intended for use.
And you leave. Disappointed.

I suppose it’s pretty ridiculous that I would miss booze the most.

If I had to say what specifically I would miss most… It would be a good single malt scotch.

And in the interest of actually answering the question…

I would miss a double meat double cheese Whataburger.

I know that the calories in one of those are disgusting. It’s my only food weakness. I only allow myself like 3 a year, but I figure if I was in prison I could afford the caloric intake.

Its a wonderful thing when you realize that you still have the ability to surprise yourself. 
Makes you wonder what else you can do that you've forgotten about.

In an attempt to spice up my journal I have been posting pictures lately. So I thought I would post a few from this weekend.




I look hotter when I drive my moms car.


Honey loves Keenan.


My friends are stoners.


He loves her, shes married to someone else.


Drunkish.
 

*edit to last entry: (minus Michael C Hall) (added David Duchovny)

There was a Californication marathon here this week to gear up for the new season and I just cant get enough of him.

Now that I have been without him for so long I can't believe I was with him for so long. 
Everyday I'm discovering new pieces of me. 
Guess this is all part of growing up.
But damn, my life is good. I count my blessings everyday. 
And, I feel more beautiful than ever. 

I haven't read any of your journals in ages, that's soon about to change. 
This summer has just been somethin' else. 

!

Apparently I am the healthy middle ground kind of girl. I'm just a pragmatic elitist. hah. But I do think its very true that I am 50% Concerned about self and 50% Concerned about others. Good to know.

Upheaval may feel unsettling (to say the least), but it also supplies many opportunities that may not come again. Chaos helps give birth to a new and better world order. Figure out how to make the most of this time.
